30-3-4 Technical Review Committee
30-3-4.1 Authority and Establishment
A planning board known as the Technical Review Committee (TRC) is hereby established pursuant to NCGS 160D-301:
however, the TRC shall not be subject to Article V of Chapter 2 of the Greensboro Code of Ordinances.
(Amended by Ord. 20-099 on 9/1/20 and Ord. 21-127 on 8/17/21)
Effective on: 8/17/2021
30-3-4.2 Membership
A. The Technical Review Committee is composed of 8 members with one representative from each of the following
departments (divisions):
1. Planning (Administration);
2. Planning (Current Planning);
3. Engineering and Inspections (Engineering);
4. Parks and Recreation;
5. Fire Department;
6. Transportation;
7. Water Resources (Engineering); and
8. Water Resources (Stormwater).
